LawleyTest              Likelihood Ratio Tests for equality of last
                        $n-K$ eigenvalues.
ZG                      Automatic Dimensionality Selection from the
                        Scree Plot via Profile Likelihood
elbowEigen              Alternative methods based on the detection of
                        elbow in sample eigenvalues.
get_data_singular       Simulate Data from Eigenvalue Structure
loglk                   Profile log-likelihood of the PPCA model with
                        sample eigenvalues.
